*>Common Db2 routines
*>****************************************************************
*>    EXEC SQL INCLUDE CSDB2RPY END-EXEC
*>vvv-> file: C:\Users\Sethulekshmi.Pishara\Work\LiberTools\CLERITY\Converter\aws_cards_demo\sources\cpy\CSDB2RPY.cpy
*>*****************************************************************
*> CardDemo - Common Procedures for Db2
